    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Adventurer's Armory 2 pg. 9</em></p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\">Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 25 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 2 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d3 (small), 1d4 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> 18-20/x2; <strong>Range</strong> -; <strong>Type</strong> S; <strong>Special</strong> see text</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Light; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Blades, Light</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3><p>Meant for quick strikes and slashes, this long, slender knife is incredibly sharp along one edge. Drow swashbucklers and assassins are particularly fond of these weapons. A confirmed critical hit or successful sneak attack with a drow razor deals an additional 2 points of damage; this damage is precision damage and is not multiplied on a critical hit. A character with the drow's weapon familiarity racial trait treats the drow razor as a martial weapon.</p>"
